              No questions asked. We'll remove the agent and you owe nothing. Your satisfaction is our priority.
            </div>
          </details>
        </MotionReveal>
        
        <MotionReveal client:visible delay={0.4}>
          <details class="glass glass-reflection" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <summary style="padding: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; min-height: 44px; display: flex; align-items: center;">Can I customize the AI agent's behavior?</summary>
            <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem; color: var(--muted);">
              Absolutely. Each agent is built specifically for your workflow and can be fine-tuned during the pilot period.
            </div>
          </details>
        </MotionReveal>
        
        <MotionReveal client:visible delay={0.5}>
          <details class="glass glass-reflection" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <summary style="padding: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; min-height: 44px; display: flex; align-items: center;">What security measures are in place?</summary>
            <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem; color: var(--muted);">
              OAuth-only access, least privilege permissions, full audit logging, and instant revocation capabilities.
            </div>
          </details>
        </MotionReveal>
        
        <MotionReveal client:visible delay={0.6}>
          <details class="glass glass-reflection" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <summary style="padding: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; min-height: 44px; display: flex; align-items: center;">How much does it cost after the pilot?</summary>
            <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem; color: var(--muted);">
              Pricing is based on usage and value delivered. We'll discuss options during your pilot period.
