          </p>
          
          <!-- Calendly placeholder -->
          <div class="glass glass-reflection" style="padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            <p style="color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">ðŸ“… Schedule your free audit</p>
            <a href="https://calendly.com/your-calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="button glass-reflection" style="background: var(--brand); border: none; color: white; font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 1rem 2rem; min-height: 44px;">
